595
00:43:15,084 --> 00:43:17,832
No. Whatever happens, we go through it together.

596
00:43:17,833 --> 00:43:20,123
I told you I'd protect you.

597
00:43:20,463 --> 00:43:23,723
- But... - Go. Hurry.

598
00:43:26,373 --> 00:43:30,323
Don't! Don't hurt me!

599
