609
00:44:18,005 --> 00:44:19,005
Don't hurt him.

610
00:44:24,273 --> 00:44:25,362
Don't worry about others.

611
00:44:25,363 --> 00:44:26,763
Just focus on surviving.

612
00:44:28,923 --> 00:44:32,723
