656
00:49:43,213 --> 00:49:45,293
He planned everything.

657
00:49:45,949 --> 00:49:47,229
Get out of there now...

658
00:49:57,643 --> 00:49:59,537
As discussed,

659
00:50:02,213 --> 00:50:04,763
