733
00:55:30,123 --> 00:55:31,492
Umm...

734
00:55:31,493 --> 00:55:33,392
Hey, that's cool.

735
00:55:33,393 --> 00:55:35,643
A lot of people here don't go to school either.

736
00:55:36,693 --> 00:55:38,542
KFC is here.

737
00:55:38,543 --> 00:55:40,323
KFC is here!

738
00:55:41,453 --> 00:55:44,122
